    "name": "Spry Ambusher",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat </b>The monk drinks her <i>potion of mage armor </i>and applies her <i>oil of magic weapon</i>.<br/><b>During Combat </b>The rogue uses Acrobatics skill to move through combat, helping allies flank.<br/><b>Base Statistics </b>Without <i>mage armor </i>and <i>magic weapon</i>, the monk\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>18, touch 17, flat-footed 16; <b>Melee </b>kama +5 (1d4+1)."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "These gnomes often protect gnome communities in groups that skirmish in the name of their lawful lord."
        }
